<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Harp2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Harp,</orth> vb. 1) tr. to touch, to hit: <cit><quote>thou hast --ed my fear aright,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 4.1.74" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 1, 74</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) intr. with <emph>on,</emph> to dwell on, to recur incessantly to the same theme: <bibl n="shak. mm 5.64" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.364" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 364</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.3.260" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 3, 260</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.189" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 189</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.13.142" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 13, 142</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>